  "text": "The metabonomics study of CUMS model of depression has already been studied on the same sample by [CITATION_1] HNMR and UHPLC-RP/MS [CITATION_2] . Here, we developed a HILIC-UHPLC/MS method for the global polar metabolic profiling of plasma, so as to provide the supplement of the metabonomics study in depression study of CUMS model, which has been widely used for studying clinical depression and evaluating antidepressant effects of diverse drugs.",
